.ue 2
                                                                       $.#$
Forts.: <Aug 57>*
In a harry I quickly send these letters just received the one of Dr Barth
was in a very thik enveloppe.

Mr Pfleiderer had news; but I know not what

This morning Mrs Hoch is somewhat better.

We have plenty rain and wind; you will have been wet, I fear, David having
reached and is a strong boy I know from the Inspector s letter

Now Adieu
.fo -
                     yours J Gundert


